'''Security Guides''' worked in the [[Learning Circle]] and the [[Re-Learning Circle]] on [[Kegan/Legends|Kegan]], teaching the students the way of the [[General Good]]. They guarded both circles and stopped children from getting out. [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Siri Tachi/Legends|Siri Tachi]] encountered a type of Security Guide, the [[Truant Guide]], during a [[Truant Sweep]] when they were mistaken for school children and were stunned and then carried to the Learning Circle. Security Guides also helped in the brainwashing process in the Re-Learning Circle.

